      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «مَا اِشْتَرَى أَحَدٌ دَابَّةً إِلاَّ قَالَتْ: اَللَّهُمَّ اِجْعَلْهُ بِي رَحِيماً »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2478 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"No one purchases an animal except that it says: 'O Allah (swt), make him merciful to me.'\""
        ]
      }
